No. 10-8382 (10A700). Leroy White, Petitioner v. Alabama. 562 U.S. 1175, 131 S. Ct. 991,

178 L. Ed. 2d 820,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 612. January 13, 2011.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death, pre*821sented to Justice Thomas, and by him referred to the Court, denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Alabama denied.
